  description: >
    This section captures behavioral or mental health records, including psychiatric evaluations,
    therapy sessions, and psychological assessments. These details are vital for understanding 
    a patientâ€™s mental health status and the care provided by specialized professionals.

  fields:
    behavioralHealthId:
